Package: mcMCMCglmm
Title: Multi-core MCMCglmm models
Version: 0.2.4
Authors@R: person("Joel"    , "Pick"           , email = "joel.l.pick@gmail.com"             , role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: R package to provide wrapper functions for the MCMCglmm R package, that allow multi-chain models to be run in parallel.
